2015-01-02 PRELIMINARY FOR NEXT RELEASE OF ALIEN ARENA

Distribution package maintainers please note that the installation is
substantially modified compared to Version 7.66:

1) The botinfo subdirectory is now a subdirectory of the data1
directory.

2) The user-writeable data directory is named `cor-games' and honors
XDG_DATA_HOME.

Please see the INSTALL document for details.

